REM windows_sysinfo.duck
REM Opens the Windows System Information panel via Win+Pause/Break.
REM Quick way to display device name, OS version, RAM, and processor.
REM Works on Windows 10 and 11. No Run dialog needed.
REM Copy to: /sdcard/lab/ble/blueduck/scripts/

HUMAN_MODE OFF

REM Win+Pause opens About / System Information directly
GUI PAUSE
